teams are both in the Final Four in their respective basketball
tournaments. No school has ever won the men's and women's NCCA
titles in the same season, but Duke has a chance. By Ira Berkow.
</P>
<P>
   BKC-OBRIEN (Undated) _ Feature on Jim O'Brien, the coach of Ohio
State, a surprise Final Four team in the NCAA tournament. O'Brien
will go up against Connecticut's Jim Calhoun on Saturday, and
Calhoun has beaten O'Brien the last 18 times they coached against
each other. By Judy Battista.
