<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-24 01:01 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1881 &Cx1f; taf-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-EDIT-OBSERVER-NYT &LR;      03-24 0818
