<P>
   &UR; CRACKING DOWN ON CENTRAL EUROPE'S NASTY NEO-NAZIS &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Moved as BC-NASTY-SKINHEADS-EUROPE-ECONOMIST-NYTSF...850 words &QL; 
