</P>
<P>
   &UR; BIZ &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; ARCH-RIVALS ORACLE, MICROSOFT COMING TO BLOWS OVER DATABASES &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (EDITORS: Note 150-word optional trim at 825) &QL;
