   WITH: CYBERSPICE -- During the Easter/Passover season, which is
one of the most significant and meaningful times of the year for
both Christians and Jews, the Internet presents a wonderful
opportunity for each to deepen their understanding of the other.
(Parham, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
