   ENTERTAINMENT-ARTS
</P>
<P>
   VIDEO-OSCARS _ A celebration of Oscar winners. A rundown of past
great videos from Sunday's best acting winners. (Ringel-Gillespie,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   VIDEO-WEEKBEST _ Video of the week: ``Pleasantville.'' Grade: B.
(Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   VIDEO-SPOTLIGHT _ Spotlight on William H. Macy of
``Pleasantville.'' (Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   VIDEO-JUSTOUT _ New releases: ``Mighty Joe Young'' (Grade: C-);
``Firelight'' (Grade: B) plus video collector. (Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   VIDEO-NEXT _ Upcoming: ``Everest,'' ``Futuresport,'' ``American
History X.'' (Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
