   NATIONAL NEWS (``a'' category)
</P>
<P>
   CALIF-MISSING (Sonora, Calif.) _ Bombarded with tips, FBI agents
are questioning men with histories of criminal violence to
eliminate suspects in the disappearance of a mother and two
teenager girls and the murders of at least two of them. By ERIC
BRAZIL and JIM HERRON ZAMORA.
</P>
<P>
   GAYS-METHODISTS (San Francisco) _ The United Methodist Church
has filed charges against 69 of its Northern California and Nevada
pastors for going against church law and blessing a lesbian couple.
By CAROL NESS.
</P>
<P>
   GAYS-SCOUTS (San Francisco) _ A 22-year employee of the Boy
Scouts is suing the organization, saying his boss hired private
investigators to grill his co-workers and friends about his sexual
orientation and then fired him because he is gay. By CAROL NESS.
</P>
