 &HT;    Spotlight on. . .
 &HT;    Staff reports
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   William H. Macy (`Pleasantville')
</P>
<P>
   ``Boogie Nights'' Getting tired of his hot-to-trot wife's antics
in this high-powered drama about the porn industry.
</P>
<P>
   ``Fargo'' Plotting one of the worst crimes of the century in the
Coen brothers' Oscar-winning film.
