   UNDATED _ Now that the 1999 Oscarcast has finally concluded _
how long did the show run this year, three days? _ I can offer my
assessment of the festivities: ``Zzzzzzzzzzzz...'' By BILL
THOMPSON. Story will move in ``k'' commentary category. &QL; 
