<P>
   &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
AMWEST-DEAL (Phoenix) - Details of a tentative agreement for the
America West flight attendants are to be released. By PETER
CORBETT. Story will move in the ``F' category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
MONTINI-COLUMN (Phoenix) - The death of 13-year-old Gricelda Zamora
was unspeakably gruesome and painful, but it was not complicated.
We're about to make it appear complicated, but it wasn't. We can't
stop ourselves. Well-meaning people have demanded an investigation
into the needless death of the 6th grade cheerleader. No
investigation is necessary. We know exactly why it happened.
Gricelda Zamora died because she was poor. By E.J. MONTINI. Story
will move in the ``A'' and ``K'' categories. &QL; 
