about seeing a naked lady at the gym would cause such a stir? Not
me for one, but plenty of people wrote me letters. Many of them
were nice (nearly all written by women), but the rest were real
NASTY (nearly all written by men). While I'm sure most nudity
enthusiasts are nice people, the ones I heard from were a roguish
lot, mean critters with poison tongues and boiling blood. For folks
who don't think twice about unveiling themselves in the wide open,
