Hedda Gabler in them,'' says actress Annette Bening, who is
fulfilling her ambition to play the complicated heroine on stage.
By Reed Johnson. 

<TEXT>
<P>
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-03-24-99 1933EST &QL; 
</TRAILER>
