<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    DESPITE CONFIDENCE, U.S. MILITARY WARY OF RISKS IN KOSOVO
CAMPAIGN
 &HT;    EDs: With US-KOSOVO-0325.
